  <entry>
    <id>https://github.com/pocket-id/pocket-id/releases/tag/v0.48.0</id>
    <title>New release for Pocket ID: v0.48.0</title>
    <updated>2025-04-18T12:34:56-04:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>pocket-id/pocket-id</name>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;[!WARNING]&lt;br /&gt;
This release fixes a bug where the callback URL wasn't validated correctly. It's recommended to update to this version.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Features&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;add gif support for logo and background image (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pocket-id/pocket-id/commit/56a8b5d0c02643f869b77cf8475ddf2f9473880b"&gt;56a8b5d&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;disable/enable users (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pocket-id/pocket-id/issues/437"&gt;#437&lt;/a&gt; by @kmendell)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Bug Fixes&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;add "type" as reserved claim (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pocket-id/pocket-id/commit/0111a58dac0342c5ac2fa25a050e8773810d2b0a"&gt;0111a58&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;callback URL doesn't get rejected if it starts with a different string (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pocket-id/pocket-id/commit/f0dce41fbc5649b3a8fe65de36ca20efa521b880"&gt;f0dce41&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;profile picture empty for users without first or last name (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pocket-id/pocket-id/issues/449"&gt;#449&lt;/a&gt; by @kmendell)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;user querying fails on global audit log page with Postgres (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pocket-id/pocket-id/commit/84f1d5c906ec3f9a74ad3d2f36526eea847af5dd"&gt;84f1d5c&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://github.com/pocket-id/pocket-id/releases/tag/v0.48.0" rel="alternate"/>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <id>https://github.com/pocket-id/pocket-id/releases/tag/v0.49.0</id>
    <title>New release for Pocket ID: </title>
    <updated>2025-04-20T14:03:03-04:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>pocket-id/pocket-id</name>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;h3&gt;Features&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;add ability to send login code via email (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pocket-id/pocket-id/issues/457"&gt;#457&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;add description to callback URL inputs (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pocket-id/pocket-id/commit/eb689eb56ec9eaf8b0fb1485040e26f841b9225d"&gt;eb689eb&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;send email to user when api key expires within 7 days (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pocket-id/pocket-id/issues/451"&gt;#451&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Bug Fixes&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;disable animations not respected on authorize and logout page (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pocket-id/pocket-id/commit/e571996cb57d04232c1f47ab337ad656f48bb3cb"&gt;e571996&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;hide alternative sign in button if user is already authenticated (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pocket-id/pocket-id/commit/4e05b82f02740a4bae07cec6c6a64acd34ca0fc3"&gt;4e05b82&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;locale change in dropdown doesn't work on first try (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pocket-id/pocket-id/commit/60bad9e9859d81c9967e6939e1ed10a65145a936"&gt;60bad9e&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;remove limit of 20 callback URLs (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pocket-id/pocket-id/commit/c37a3e0ed177c3bd2b9a618d1f4b0709004478b0"&gt;c37a3e0&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://github.com/pocket-id/pocket-id/releases/tag/v0.49.0" rel="alternate"/>
  </entry>
